### **Transcript**

This year's summer speaking tour has come to an end, with presentations at **Athens SEO, Croatia SEO Summit, CAMPIXX Berlin, Peec AI,** and **Search 'n Stuff London**.
The main topic was **"How SEO & GEO Work Together – Do Great GEO Without Destroying Your SEO."**
The presentation explained that many strategies websites use to improve visibility in **AI Search (GEO)** are actually harming their traditional SEO performance. Since AI models rely heavily on information from high-ranking search results, declining SEO performance can also reduce visibility in AI-generated answers.
The session also covered practical recommendations on what businesses should prioritize and shared the speaker's current approach to **Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)** and **Generative Engine Optimization (GEO).**
The presentation slides have been uploaded to **SlideShare** and are available through the link in the comments.
